Additional country comapred to the previous update

column1: Note:  For those countries where annual data are not yet availalbe for 2022, annual averages of monthly or quarterly inflation in 2022 with available data are included instead. For those countries where energy consumer price index is not available, consumer price index for the sector on housing, fuel, water, electricity, gas and other fuels (COICOP 04) is used as proxy for energy prices.
